snippet.title: Miniclip: Detonator (Flash Game) Gameplay
snippet.description:
This one is so off the hook to me. I mean I can't even do level 3, and move my character 1.5 second at a certain time when I should move. Other than that, Miniclip is the one who developed this super old flash game. I bet the kids who played this flash game won the entire thing.
